{"id":65538,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/汇市分析-投机商的欧元空头头寸创纪录新高/","date":"2010-05-02T03:00:04Z","modified":"2010-05-02T03:00:04Z","title":"[汇市分析] 投机商的欧元空头头寸创纪录新高","content":"<p><span></span></p>\n<div style=\"float:left;width:28px;color:#c74b15;border:0px solid #000000;margin:0px 0px 0px 0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 0px;line-height:140%;font-size:28px;font-weight:bolder\">据</div>\n<p>周五公布的数据显示，投机商的欧元空头头寸大幅增加，创纪录新高，有关欧元区主权债务危机的忧虑影响了欧元走势，激发了投资者的不安情绪。</p>\n<p>据Scotia Bank对美国商品期货委员会(Commodity Futures Trading Commission)周五下午尾段公布的每周交易者持仓报告的分析显示，截至周二的一周，投机商的欧元净空头头寸从之前一周的120亿美元增加至147亿美元。</p>\n<p></p>\n<div>\n<div style=\"border-top:4px solid #b0cada;margin:12px 5px 3px 0px;font-size:14px;padding:3px 0px 0px 3px;font-weight:bold;color:#303030\">相关阅读</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100304/hrd103048.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">做空可以，针对欧元不行？</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-03-04</span><br /><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100303/bus103925.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">美国调查做空欧元之赌</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-03-03</span><br /><a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100226/beu121910.asp?source=article\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"margin:12px 5px 5px 5px;padding-left:8px;background:no-repeat left;font-size:14px;color:#093d72\">顶尖对冲基金大举做空欧元</a> <span style=\"color:#666;font-size:12px;font-family:arial\">2010-02-26</span></div>\n<div style=\"border-bottom:1px #ccc solid;padding-bottom:5px;padding-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100501/../img/more_arrows.gif\" width=\"5\"> 本文涉及股票或公司</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-size:14px\">\n<div style=\"background-color:EEF2F4;padding:8px